Definition: having or showing a tender and considerate and helpful nature
Example: used especially of persons and their behavior; kind to sick patients; a kind master; kind words showing understanding and sympathy; thanked her for her kind letter
Synonyms: noun, attribute, kindness, act, UNKIND, CONSIDERATE, BENIGN, GOOD-NATURED, MERCIFUL, SOFT, having, or, showing, a, tender, and, considerate, helpful, nature, used, especially, of, persons, their, behavior, kind, to, sick, patients, master, words, understanding, sympathy, thanked, her, for, letter
Category: adj.all
